                <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn" rendition="class:83231 maturity:83213">
<p><milestone type="pagelike" unit="face" n="A"/><label xml:lang="eng">Face A</label>
   <lb n="A1"/>neḥ bhūmi ta roḥh neḥ vvaṁ Āc ti mān {5} ya nu qnak ta gi viṣaya phoṅ ta vāda $circleSmall pratyaya
   <lb n="A2"/>{6} nā mok pan[dva]l loñ bhadraśiva loñ vrahmaśiva loñ ravi loñ candra
</p>
                   <p><milestone type="pagelike" unit="face" n="B"/><label xml:lang="eng">Face B</label>
   <lb n="B1"/>{10} nirṇṇaya toy Uttamasāha $circleSmall man vāp pān[dava] {3}
   <lb n="B2"/>{15} svaṁ prasāda gi pi ros ta gi pi vvaṁ vraḥ pre {3}
                      <lb n="B3"/>{14} vraḥ mattavāraṇa $circleSmall pre cār Iss śākha saṁnva[t] {1}
                      <lb n="B4"/>{6} pre pratyaya dau saṅ gol praśasta viṅ ta gi bhūmi ta roḥh neḥh $circleSmall pre ni
</p>
                   <p><milestone type="pagelike" unit="face" n="C"/><label xml:lang="eng">Face C</label>
   <lb n="C1"/>yama daha mān(·) {2}
   <lb n="C2"/>vāp· pāndava ta thve vāda bhū-
   <lb n="C3"/>mi neḥ ley· pre saṁlā-
   <lb n="C4"/>p· qyat si stāp· vyavahāra
   <lb n="C5"/>ley(·) ta qnau nā mā-
   <lb n="C6"/>n· vraḥ karuṇā {4}
   <lb n="C7"/>neḥha ($circleSmall) mratāñ· khlo-
   <lb n="C8"/>ñ· śrī vīrendravarmma $circleSmall mratā-
   <lb n="C9"/>ñ· khloñ· śrī vīrendrādhi-
   <lb n="C10"/>pativarmma $circleSmall mratāñ(·) khlo[ñ·]
   <lb n="C11"/>śrī mahīdharavarmma $circleSmall [mratā]-
   <lb n="C12"/>ñ· khloñ· śrī jayā[yu]-
   <lb n="C13"/>ddhavarmma $circleSmall mratāñ(·) khlo[ñ·]
   <lb n="C14"/>śrī narapatīndrava[rmma $circleSmall mratā]-
   <lb n="C15"/>ñ· khloñ· śrī dhara{3}-
   <lb n="C16"/>varmma $circleSmall mratāñ· śrī {3}-
   <lb n="C17"/>rimathana $circleSmall mratāñ(·) {3}-
   <lb n="C18"/>ndrārimathana $circleSmall mratā[ñ·] {3}-
   <lb n="C19"/>nakesari $circleSmall mratā[ñ· śrī]
   <lb n="C20"/>dharaṇīndraparākrama $circleSmall [mra]-
   <lb n="C21"/>tāñ· śrī dharaṇīndropa-
   <lb n="C22"/>kalpa $circleSmall kaṁsteṅ· Añ(·) guṇa-
   <lb n="C23"/>doṣa $circleSmall mratāñ· śrī mahe-
   <lb n="C24"/>ndrasiṅha $circleSmall mratāñ· śrī vi-
   <lb n="C25"/>kramasiṅha $circleSmall mratā-
   <lb n="C26"/>ñ· śrī rajendrasiṅha $circleSmall mratā-
   <lb n="C27"/>ñ· śrī parākramasiṅha $circleSmall ri
   <lb n="C28"/>vraḥ sabhā ta paṅgaṁ th(p)[vaṅ· nive]-
   <lb n="C29"/>dana $circleSmall mratāñ· {4}
   <lb n="C30"/>tabhaktivallabha $circleSmall {4}
   <lb n="C31"/>vrahmayogisV {4}
   <lb n="C32"/>vāp· rudrabhāva {3} [vya]-
   <lb n="C33"/>vahāra ta vāp ta {3}
   <lb n="C34"/>taṁ sruk kaṁveṅ ta {3}
   <lb n="C35"/>noḥha chvāt· ma{3}-
   <lb n="C36"/>la $circleSmall pandval[[·]] vraḥ śāsa[na]
   <lb n="C37"/>Oy· bhūmi ta roḥha
   <lb n="C38"/>neḥha viṅ ta vāp tapoma-
   <lb n="C39"/>ya $circleSmall
</p>
